column5: Some great new stuff this month... LOOK at the writers we have.  What a group!!  Downsizing Tactics for Smallmouth Bass By Tim Allard  Fish of a Thousand Casts? By Craig Ritchie  When Smallies Go Cray-Zee By Rob Romberg  The Surface is an Edge By Pete Maina  Finding Weedline Largemouth Bass By J.P. DeRose  Get North! Stressed? need a vacation?  Visit Get North to find your Northern Ontario get-away!  Fishing Lodge Classifieds Come fish your heart out at one of these many Lodges, Camps and Resorts.  Also, please let me know what you think..
Too impressive, Bud! I'll wait till tonight to read this when I have the time to enjoy it. Congrats on the stellar lineup.
A stellar line up of outdoor writers indeed. I'll get back to reading it all of it with my morning java fix. No doubt it'll be educational.
